        <strong>Questions?</strong>
        <p>Reach out to your ActiveCampaign affiliate manager via PartnerStack or email <a href="mailto:psaffiliates@activecampaign.com" style="color:var(--moss-600);">psaffiliates@activecampaign.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider">

    <!-- SUBMIT -->
    <div class="cta-block">
        <h3>Ready to create?</h3>
